# Cursor Rules – DarkBot.Net (Clean Architecture)

Desktop-бот для DarkOrbit: Avalonia UI + Frida bridge + Electron client.

## Слои

| Проект | Роль | Зависит от |
|--------|------|------------|
| `DarkBot.Net.Core` | Контракты (`I*Api`, `IGameFridaProbe`), модели, Options | — |
| `DarkBot.Net.Application` | Bot loop, managers, `I*AppService` | Core |
| `DarkBot.Net.Infrastructure` | Frida, Electron, Login, Backpage, Config | Core, Application |
| `DarkBot.Net.Presentation` | Avalonia Views/ViewModels, composition root | Application, Infrastructure |

```text
Presentation → Application, Infrastructure (DI wiring)
Infrastructure → Application, Core
Application → Core
Core → (ничего)
```

## DarkBot.Net.Core

- Интерфейсы: `Managers/`, `Game/`, `Auth/`
- Модели: entities, Frida snapshots, login data
- `Common/OperationResult.cs`
- `Options/GameApiOptions.cs`, `LoginOptions.cs`
- ❌ Нет реализаций, HttpClient, Process, Avalonia

## DarkBot.Net.Application

- `Contracts/I*AppService` — фасады для UI
- `Services/Bot/` — BotLoopService, BotRuntime, managers
- `Services/Game/`, `Services/Auth/` — AppService реализации
- `Extensions/DependencyInjection.cs` — `AddApplication()`, Scrutor `*AppService`
- ❌ Нет Frida, Electron, HTTP, UI

## DarkBot.Net.Infrastructure

- `Game/` — FridaGameApi, DarkorbitClientLauncher, hosted services
- `Auth/` — LoginService, BackpageService, captcha
- `Config/` — ConfigSetting, StubConfigApi
- `DependencyInjection.cs` — `AddInfrastructure(configuration)`
- C# **не читает память процесса** — только snapshot из Frida WS/HTTP

## DarkBot.Net.Presentation

- ViewModels вызывают **только** `I*AppService`
- `Program.cs` — Generic Host + Avalonia
- `AddApplication()` + `AddInfrastructure()` + `AddPresentationUi()`
- ❌ ViewModels не зависят от Infrastructure-типов

## Игровой путь (Frida-only)

```text
DarkBot.Net/Darkorbit-client (Electron)
  → avm_bridge (:44570)
  → Infrastructure.Game (FridaGameApi)
  → Core.IGameFridaProbe
  → Application managers (HeroManager, MapManager, …)
  → BotLoopService @ 10 Hz
```

## AppService-фасады

| Интерфейс | Назначение |
|-----------|------------|
| `ILoginAppService` | Логин credentials/SID |
| `IGameLaunchAppService` | Запуск клиента + Frida connect |
| `IBotControlAppService` | Start/pause/stop бота |
| `IBotStatusAppService` | Snapshot для UI |

## Запрещено

- ❌ `Core → Infrastructure` или `Application → Infrastructure` (compile-time)
- ❌ Плагины/DLL hot-reload (удалены из v2)
- ❌ `.Result` / `.Wait()` на Task
- ❌ Логировать SID, пароли, токены

## Тесты

- `tests/DarkBot.Net.Application.Tests` — bot loop, managers
- `tests/DarkBot.Net.Core.Tests` — контракты/модели (если нужно)
- Infrastructure tests — Login, Backpage
